Dorothy Boyd https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dorothy_Boyd 0 Dorothy Boyd (14 April 1907 – 1996) was an English film actress. She appeared in 38 films between 1926 and 1940. She was born in Sanderstead, Surrey, England and died in England. Dorothy_Boyd ( 14_April_1907 – 1996 ) was an_English_film_actress . She appeared in 38_films between 1926_and_1940 .
